lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, Nov. 9 -- Administration supporters, confident that next week-end will find American ships free to sail any seas, urged today that speedy steps be taken to "deliver the goods" to Great Britain and Russia.
abstract: Sen Bridges urges no immediate action on war zone lifting
